title: For Sale:  M885  info
postcontent:
For everyone calling the M855 green tip penetrator . Steel, steel core, or armor piercing.
Cut one of the tips open ,I it you will find a small pyramid shape piece of tungsten. this is all that is in the tip. Yes they will penetrate steel . But I would not try to shoot my way into an armor car with them. Specially like the car that the President is driven around in.
Now if anyone ready want armor piecing bullet's ,I have about 200 30 caliber bullets for 30-06 /308. I might consider selling these for a tidy sum, But the offer has to be right. And yes these are the same military bullet that were loaded in the ammo for the WWII M-1 Garand, used in the Korean war and WWII. And they will knock a hole in at least 1/2 inch steel plate. like cutting through butter!

postcontent:
For sale is a like new Adams Arms Conversion Kit. XLP Gas block, low mass nickel boron carrier, this is the top notch kit from Adams. Used in an experimental 300 blackout setup, but didn't quite work out. Less than 50 rounds through the kit. All you need to add is a bolt, firing pin, cam, and upper bushing (the one in the kit was installed in my upper). Obviously this does not include the barrel, upper, etc. This is just the conversion kit. Info below. Will ship on your dime and you will have to cover paypal fees.

Info from Adams:

This system will work with .223/5.56 x 45 mm NATO.

Kit includes:

    Patented One-Piece Bolt Carrier (Nibx and low mass)
    XLP Multi-Adjustable Low Profile Gas Block
    Gas Plug
    Upper Receiver Bushing (you will need one of these if your upper is not adams arms brand)
    Bushing Installation Rod
    Bolt Spring
    Drive Rod with Bushing and Spring
    Installation DVD

The Adams Arms Piston System:

    A short stroke free floating piston system.
    Is Self-Cleaning.
    Carbon and gases are expelled forward, away from operator.
    Corrosive resistant coating processes.
    Harmonics are not transferred into the barrel.
    Adjustable gas settings for various applications.
    Doesn't vent directly to atmospheric pressure; this eliminates flash signature and super sonic crack which is optimal for night vision and suppresses fire.

This system requires a pistol gas length (4.846" from barrel extension to shoulder) and a .750" gas seat.

We recommend using a standard barrel nut or barrel nut with similar measurements for proper fit and function of the kit. Many aftermarket proprietary barrel nuts do not offer the clearance for the drive rod or proper seating of the spring and bushing.
